node.title: Police trying to establish if others involved in Cleo Smith abduction
node.alt: A police officer loads large paper bags into a trailer.
node.description: Detectives say they expect to remain in Carnarvon for at least a week as they try to determine if more than one person was involved in Cleo Smith's abduction.
node.content:
["Police say they are trying to determine if more than one person\u00a0was involved in the\u00a0abduction of four-year-old Cleo Smith, who was missing from a family camping trip for 18 days before being found in a Carnarvon house.", "Touching down at Carnarvon airport on Monday morning, about 900 kilometres north of Perth, one of the officers who rescued Cleo from the locked house said the investigation was going well, but there was still work to do.\u00a0", "\u201cThe focus this week is for us to ascertain if there was anyone else involved that\u2019s why we\u2019re still here,\u201d Detective Senior Sergeant\u00a0Cameron Blaine said.\u00a0", "He called for anyone who who had contact with Cleo\u2019s alleged abductor, Terence Darrell Kelly, to come forward.\u00a0", "\"We just ask that if there was anyone that had any contact with Mr Kelly, whether you saw him, whether you met with him, whether you spoke to him on the phone during the relevant period, to please make yourself known to police,\" he said.", "Detective Senior Sergeant\u00a0Blaine was part of a team of detectives who returned to Carnarvon on Monday to continue with their investigation after spending the weekend back in Perth.\u00a0", "He said the team was expected to stay in Carnarvon for at least a week.\u00a0", "Detective Blaine was one of the four officers who rescued Cleo in the early hours of Wednesday morning and asked her to confirm her name.\u00a0", "\"M-my name is Cleo,\" the preschooler memorably replied.", "
More bags taken from Terrence Kelly house
", "Meanwhile, police remain at the home where Cleo was found with detectives visiting the scene on Monday.", "On Sunday they continued to load brown paper evidence bags into two forensic vehicles parked at the taped-off crime scene.", "", "
The Carnarvon house where the four-year-old was found is being guarded by police.(ABC News: James Carmody)
", "The man charged with stealing Cleo from her family\u2019s tent at the Blowholes campsite in the early hours of Saturday\u00a0October 16 remains in a maximum security prison in Perth as he awaits his next court appearance in early December.\u00a0", "Terence Darrell Kelly was flown from Carnarvon to Perth on Friday flanked by specialist officers from the Department of Justice.\u00a0", "", "
Cleo Smith's alleged abductor Terence Kelly has been transferred to Casuarina prison\u00a0in Perth.(Facebook)
", "Mr Kelly was taken to hospital in Carnarvon twice following his arrest.\u00a0", "He appeared in the Carnarvon Magistrates Court on Thursday charged with one count of child stealing and other offences.\u00a0"]
